- Popularity is often measured by the number of views; 
- Viewer satisfaction can be gauged by the average rating given by the viewers; 
- In the context of this query, North America is a specific region of interest.

- Administrators are users with the role of 'admin' in the user roles table; 
- The view count refers to the total number of times a media content has been viewed by administrators; 
- The top 3 most viewed media content refers to the content with the highest view counts within each genre; 
- The distribution date is the date when the media content was distributed with a status of 'Completed'.
